    Fetch data from the hdf5 file

    FetchH5.Rd

    Fetch data from the hdf5 file

    Usage

    FetchH5(
  DataFile,
  MetaFile,
  name = NULL,
  features = NULL,
  slot = NULL,
  assay = NULL,
  metanames = NULL,
  reduction = NULL
)
